JOHN BARNARD BYLES , Knt. one of the Justices of Her Majesty's Court of Common Pleas;
THOMAS CHALLIS , Esq., and THOMAS QUESTED FINNIS, Esq., Aldermen of the said City;
RUSSELL GURNET , Esq., Q. C., M.P., Recorder of the said City;
JAMES ABBISS , Esq., and
ANDREW LUSK , Esq., M.P., Aldermen of the said City; THOMAS CHAMBURS, Esq., Q.C., M.P., Common Serjeant of the said City; and
ROBERT MALCOLM KERR , Esq., Judge of the Sheriffs' Court; Her Majesty's Justices of Oyer and Terminer and General Gaol Delivery of Newgate, holden for the said City, and Judges of the Central Criminal Court.
